{"tid":2397171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram 增 WhatsApp 對話記錄匯入  ","createTime":"2021-02-06T07:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T08:03:34.000Z","uid":89388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf61de48d2e33af47e17c2da3cbc76ac7ef1e4ad","tid":2397171,"uid":89388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 用戶出走潮：<br />\n<br />\n重視私隱的通訊軟體 Telegram 近日則宣佈他們新增用戶達到 1 億人，更重要的是本次更新將會加入「對話記錄匯出功能」，使用者可以從WhatsApp、LINE 以及 KokaoTalk 上搬移對話紀錄、影片、文字到 Telegram 上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTelegram 強調，在 Telegram 傳送的訊息、相片和檔案都不佔用戶手機空間，這是因為文字或任何檔案都在 Telegram 的檔案伺服器處理，Telegram 也允許用戶刪除接收或發出的任何文字訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8869c8722298069c917426da786dbc09ea06fed4","tid":2397171,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"訓咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"e013875e355ea6927c0009f2f74c1c3c5b2dd3db","tid":2397171,"uid":185631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8869c8722298069c917426da786dbc09ea06fed4","tid":2397171,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"訓咗幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"你知唔代表所有人都知既"},{"pid":"11a26bff89d828bb634c824f143945496aa04c2f","tid":2397171,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"Android好似export得好少"},{"pid":"49600153a0b25527036bdb05d8df8c867a70a6ba","tid":2397171,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e013875e355ea6927c0009f2f74c1c3c5b2dd3db","tid":2397171,"uid":185631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8869c8722298069c917426da786dbc09ea06fed4","tid":2397171,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:02:08.000Z","msg